{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very prominent people, and we were very envious of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very envious of them because-- because of their position in the SS barracks, they were able to get more food than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They never ran hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we heard, and we knew, that they were-- had, like, an underground movement-- part of an underground movement-- because they took away from the selections.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I will tell you about these selections later on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took people out of selections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were not gassed because they were too skinny.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyhow, to make a long story short, they came to the gallows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the SS officer shouted in the name of the German Reich, you know, because of activities against the German government, you are being condemned to die by hanging.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were put on the-- underneath the gallows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one shouted-- I think it was Leo Diamond-- shouted, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Don't worry comrades, we are the last ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was already in 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It must have been in October, actually, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was October 10.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was one year we were in-- in-- 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The SS officer got red in his face and told to the hangman to put his noose, los!",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The next one, I think it was Nathan, who shouted, [NON-ENGLISH   SPEECH]-- long live liberty.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And again, he was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then the third one, he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we were so elated by this defiance of-- in-- they knew they were going to hang.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And their defiance, because never, ever has it happened that we shout, in the presence of SS officers, something in defiance to them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were all so elated.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
